<Layout title="Through The Dark" description="In-dev game I'm working on">
    <Header/>
    <article class="paragraph">
        <br>
        <h1 class="text-4xl">Through The Dark</h1>
        <p>Through The Dark is a game where you play as a student alterning between reality and her dreams</p><br>
        <br>
        <p>You play as Diana, a 21 years old student. She is studying to become a biological scientist, and one night, accidentally took one of her experimental school project instead of her usual medication, and gained access to the Dream World, a mysterious place between the livings and the deads.</p>
        <br>
        <p>The game is made in C++, using SFML as an engine.</p>
      </article>

    <article class="paragraph">
        <h1 class="text-2xl">Screenshots : </h1>
